But I did not come here today merely as a mom trying to keep a sport her children love.

2895
04:50:12,500 --> 04:50:23,500
I am also a volunteer adaptive sports instructor with a non-profit group affiliated with the University of New Hampshire called Northeast Passage.

2896
04:50:23,500 --> 04:50:35,500
I teach people with disabilities how to adapt water sports so they can enjoy some of the same pastimes that we take for granted.

2897
04:50:35,500 --> 04:50:42,500
It is more than just having fun on the water for people with disabilities.

2898
04:50:42,500 --> 04:50:52,000
It is also about overcoming challenges and having a sense of accomplishment when their world is filled with obstacles.

2899
04:50:52,000 --> 04:51:06,500
In my 16 years as an instructor, I have had many tearful moms express their gratitude for making it possible for their child to be just like other kids.

2900
04:51:06,500 --> 04:51:16,000
