2901
04:51:16,000 --> 04:51:23,500
She made a list of all the things she would never be able to do.

2902
04:51:23,500 --> 04:51:34,500
But after seeing what she was capable of doing behind a boat, she planned to cross all those items off her list.

2903
04:51:34,500 --> 04:51:46,500
Most of the boats we use at Northeast Passage are wakeboats, because they are versatile and work well at different speeds and wake sizes.

2904
04:51:46,500 --> 04:51:59,000
The configuration allows family and friends to be part of the experience without getting in the way of safety personnel and equipment on the boat.

2905
04:51:59,000 --> 04:52:08,500
There are people today proposing restrictions to wakeboats that will severely impact our ability to work with disabled athletes.

2906
04:52:08,500 --> 04:52:53,500
Mobility issues can make it hard to transfer people from water to boat so often we start and end close to shore to allow for an assisted swim to shore deep water instruction and starts are harder to perform and less safe for both our instructors and our students the increased distance we would need to maintain from our support vehicles would create issues with communication, increase the time to get to a disabled participant, and increase anxiety for some of our participants, especially those with visual and hearing impairments.

2907
04:52:53,500 --> 04:53:01,500
These restrictions could make it impossible for us to teach some of our most vulnerable participants.

2908
04:53:01,500 --> 04:53:33,500
And for this reason, I you please don't pass this bill because I am on the lake all the time I see the good the bad and the ugly inconsiderate and dangerous operators are not limited to one kind of boat or water sport I've seen a bay liner run at top speed through three clearly marked buoys and end up on the rocks.

2909
04:53:33,500 --> 04:53:48,500
I've watched boats filled with people towing multiple children on one tube, circling round and round, creating huge waves to the detriment of others until heads collide and children fly.

2910
04:53:48,500 --> 04:53:54,000
It would be harmful to single out and punish one group.

2911
04:53:54,000 --> 04:54:03,500
A huge effort was made last year to educate wakeboat operators on best practices when pulling a wake surfer.

2912
04:54:03,500 --> 04:54:09,000
