2931
04:55:44,500 --> 04:55:49,000
And that has changed our market, our waterfront significantly.

2932
04:55:49,000 --> 04:55:55,500
We have a floating dock because we have many, many canoes and kayaks.

2933
04:55:55,500 --> 04:56:05,000
I think at last count there's three canoes, six or seven whitewater kayaks, and about maybe nine flatwater kayaks.

2934
04:56:05,000 --> 04:56:07,000
But no more boats.

2935
04:56:07,000 --> 04:56:09,500
I hate internal combustion engines.

2936
04:56:09,500 --> 04:56:18,000
But having a floating dock makes it much easier to get in and out of those boats.

2937
04:56:18,000 --> 04:56:22,500
But the wake boats have really changed the equation.

2938
04:56:22,500 --> 04:56:40,500
and I am no longer able to walk on my dock when there are wakeboats going around our cove because it bounces the dock around so much that I can no longer stand up straight safely.

2939
04:56:40,500 --> 04:56:43,500
