3022
05:05:19,500 --> 05:05:24,500
I guess I represent the little guys, the little lakes.

3023
05:05:24,500 --> 05:05:39,000
We are 345 acres in a figure eight configuration, long and narrow, if you will, with a no-wake zone in the middle and two small ponds on either side.

3024
05:05:39,000 --> 05:05:51,000
As a result, this bill, if passed as constituted, would be detrimental to the wake surfing sport on Cobbett's Pond, which is quite robust.

3025
05:05:51,000 --> 05:06:11,000
There are more than 20 wake surf boats on our lake today, all of which owned by family members, and it is the quintessential family sport, as many here have talked about today, so I won't get into those details.

3026
05:06:11,000 --> 05:06:50,000
What I would like to say is that the sport is relatively young, and with anything new, you're going to have your hiccups and speed bumps, and there's a learning curve associated with it, and I think the Wake Responsibility Program is a great step forward in the education of people on how to more responsibly use these powerful boats for the betterment of everyone and the enjoyment of the users, but also in respect for our neighbors.

3027
05:06:50,000 --> 05:07:05,500
