3050
05:11:38,000 --> 05:11:52,500
Talk to folks with better knowledge of what's in store for that program and work on the boater education before people even get behind the wheel of the boat.

3051
05:11:52,500 --> 05:12:02,000
I think that's going to go a long way versus a premature segregation of the activity as a whole.

3052
05:12:02,000 --> 05:12:13,500
